tsclient (3.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Default GTK's renderer to cairo so the app runs without /dev/dri access.
  * Install Cinnamon applet conditionally to fix Debian builds on systems
    without the optional files.
  * Add intltool skip list to keep autopoint-based tests quiet.
  * Refresh Flatpak packaging bits for the Flathub submission.

 -- Erick Woods <erick@gnomepro.com>  Mon, 17 Nov 2025 02:15:00 -0600

